{"tid":194895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金像獎】《樹大招風》諷刺大陸貪污 拍攝前預咗被封殺","createTime":"2017-04-10T09:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T07:52:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f616b11628a5ddfb2b8b2adf2e8e7d2d4168bd78","tid":194895,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170410/large/1491757075_cfb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170410%2Flarge%2F1491757075_cfb0.jpg&h=022de5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金像獎噚日圓滿閉幕，本土電影《樹大招風》又一次成為最佳電影，仲記得上年最佳電影《十年》於片尾，寄語香港人「為時未晚」，一年後，有份於《十年》執導嘅歐文傑，連續兩年奪最佳電影。<br />\n<br />\n《樹大招風》以三位賊王嘅故事結合而成，故事講到尾，目的只係為咗諷刺大陸貪污。三位導演曾經喺接受訪問講過，拍攝時已經預咗俾大陸封殺，冇諗過有機會喺大陸上映，就算戲中有大陸場面，都係偷偷地上去拍攝。<br />\n結果一如所料，大陸封殺咗呢套電影，連噚晚金像獎都唔敢直播，眼不見為乾淨嘅程度，係大陸網站上面嘅得獎名單，都見唔到《樹大招風》個名。不過由大陸青年電影手冊舉辦嘅2016年度華語十佳影片之中，《樹大招風》就榜上有名，一度突破封鎖。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170410/56544159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170410%2F56544159&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=68da74dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170410%2F56544159&h=3a9ccd1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170410/56544159</a>"},{"pid":"1d279c946e1d4079baeeece28f33c4ea0b44286a","tid":194895,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:49:44.000Z","msg":"鎖國啦仆街"},{"pid":"5b570fea88af64d8aed1d3742c8e8d2530b0be55","tid":194895,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:53:54.000Z","msg":"繼《十年》後, 第二套最佳電影被支那封殺"},{"pid":"2b53462bccd927b3775a106dbbf7b320fbcb4392","tid":194895,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:58:02.000Z","m